# ai-sdd:begin — managed by ai-sdd-bootstrap; edits between these markers are overwritten on re-bootstrap
# Software factory runtime (the rest of .ai-sdd/ is committed)
.ai-sdd/runs/
.ai-sdd/artifacts/
# Agent-local state (NOT .agents/skills/ — that's the committed Codex repo-level skill surface).
# NOTE: .claude/ is intentionally COMMITTED in this repo (team wiki/research skills) — a maintainer
# decision overriding the bootstrap default — so it is deliberately NOT listed here.
# EXCEPTION: .claude/projects/ is per-session agent state + memory (named after the abs cwd path),
# not a team skill surface — keep it agent-local.
.claude/projects/
.codex/
# Per-vertical ignore_folders (MASTER_REQUIREMENTS → Tech stacks). __pycache__/, .venv/, dist/,
# build/, out/, .pytest_cache/ are already covered by the global Python/Node sections above; the
# scoped entries below cover the vertical-specific folders not otherwise ignored.
# Verticals map: contracts/ + operator/ + pilot/ (new dirs) · coprocessor=robot/pi-runtime · brain=robot/v5-brain
# contracts: captures
contracts/captures/
# operator: .claude out
operator/.claude/
operator/out/
# pilot (online-control harness): captures
pilot/captures/
# coprocessor (robot/pi-runtime): models captures
robot/pi-runtime/models/
robot/pi-runtime/captures/
# brain (robot/v5-brain): PROS build artifacts are handled by robot/v5-brain/v5-test/.gitignore
# ai-sdd:end
